Package: hackode
Architecture: any
Depends:
    ${shlibs:Depends},
    ${misc:Depends}
Description: Dictionary-based reversible transform CLI tools
 hackode ships the enckode/deckode command-line tools and runtime assets.
 It provides dictionary-driven reversible text/number transforms with
 gettext translations, shell completion, and man pages.
