Package: libhackode0
Section: libs
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Depends:
    ${shlibs:Depends},
    ${misc:Depends}
Description: Shared library for hackode dictionary cipher
 libhackode0 provides the runtime shared library implementing the
 dictionary-based reversible transform used by enckode/deckode and
 embeddable by other C applications.
Description-de: Laufzeitbibliothek fuer die hackode-Woerterbuchchiffre
Description-eo: Rultempa biblioteko por la hackode-vortarcifro
Description-fr: Bibliotheque d'execution pour le chiffreur dictionnaire hackode
